Download Transferencia

Source: R/download_data.R
download_transf.Rd

Download Transferencia

download_transf(year = NULL, month = NULL, ...)

Arguments

year

integer between 2013 and 2019
month

integer between 1 and 12
...

additional parameters

Value

data.frame

See also

Other Despesas Publicas: download_exec_desp

Examples
